          >Agentic AI</span
        > to transform traditional security operations into a <span class="font-semibold"
          >self-improving, self-orchestrating cyber defense ecosystem</span
        >.
      </p>
    </Fragment>
  </Content>

  <!-- Agentic AI Explanation ******* -->

  <Features2
    title="What Is an Agentic AI SOC?"
    subtitle="AI that doesn't just assist. It acts."
    columns={2}
    items={[
      {
        title: 'Independently Analyzes Threats',
        description: 'Understands attacker intent and behavior without human intervention.',
        icon: 'tabler:brain',
      },
      {
        title: 'Takes Contextual Decisions',
        description: 'Makes intelligent decisions based on full context and threat intelligence.',
        icon: 'tabler:bulb',
      },
      {
        title: 'Collaborates Across Tools',
        description: 'Correlates signals across cloud, endpoints, identity, and network seamlessly.',
        icon: 'tabler:network',
      },
      {
        title: 'Orchestrates Response Workflows',
        description: 'Runs autonomous playbooks in seconds and escalates only real incidents.',
        icon: 'tabler:robot',
      },
    ]}
  >
    <Fragment slot="bg">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-transparent"></div>
    </Fragment>
  </Features2>

  <!-- Strategic Benefits *********** -->

